/******	Defs.h ************************************************************\

Project:	Ursula (RISC OS for Risc PC II)
Component:	Configure Installer module (for SysMerge/FontMerge/BootMerge)
This file:	Macros I couln't live without

History:
Date		Who	Change
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
